hanzo-cubecl-hip
================

This crate is a fork of `cubecl-hip` 0.10.0 by Tracel Technologies Inc. / the
CubeCL Framework Contributors (https://github.com/tracel-ai/cubecl),
redistributed under its original MIT OR Apache-2.0 license (see LICENSE-MIT and
LICENSE-APACHE).

Sole modification by Hanzo AI, Inc. (manifest only; no source change):
  * The `cubecl-hip-sys` dependency is repointed to `hanzo-cubecl-hip-sys` (a
    fork of cubecl-hip-sys carrying a ROCm 7.13+ build.rs fallback) via a
    package rename that keeps every `use cubecl_hip_sys` in src/ working
    unchanged.
  * The library target is renamed from `cubecl_hip` to `hanzo_cubecl_hip`.

All Rust source under src/ is verbatim from upstream cubecl-hip 0.10.0. No
upstream authorship is claimed.

Upstream PR (against cubecl-hip-sys, the root cause):
  https://github.com/tracel-ai/cubecl-hip-sys/pull/35
